koohiiStory1: Crotch to crotch is how many pairs spend their private time together. . .
koohiiStory2: The animals boarding Noah´s Ark all came in pairs – but Noah had to carefully check the two crotches in each pair to ensure that the animals were of different sexes and thus able to further their species after the flood.
kunYomi: ふた、たぐい、ならぶ、ふたつ
myStory: cặp. đôi. hai lần thêm nữa nữa.
words: 双子(ふたご): twins, a twin
